{"id":33674,"date":"2019-01-08T20:52:13","date_gmt":"2019-01-08T10:52:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/?p=33674"},"modified":"2021-10-14T14:59:12","modified_gmt":"2021-10-14T04:59:12","slug":"nsw-489-regional","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/nsw-489-regional\/","title":{"rendered":"NSW 489 Regional"},"content":{"rendered":"[vc_row type=&#8221;in_container&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; text_color=&#8221;dark&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; row_border_radius_applies=&#8221;bg&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; shape_divider_position=&#8221;bottom&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221;][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; tablet_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; phone_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]The <strong>Skilled Regional nominated (489)<\/strong> visa is a provisional skilled visa that allows applicants to live and work in regional NSW for up to<strong> 4 years<\/strong>. Currently, there are 9 regions\u00a0participating in the NSW 489 program.<\/p>\n<p>Each regional area publishes its own skilled occupation list with the occupations that are in demand. The information below is a summary of the status of each region.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Central West<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed.\u00a0The Central West Skills Occupation List will re-open in March 2019.<br \/>\n<a href=\"http:\/\/www.rdacentralwest.org.au\/visas\/visa-489\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http:\/\/www.rdacentralwest.org.au\/visas\/visa-489\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Far South Coast<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed.\u00a0Applications for the Skilled Regional Sponsored Visa (SRS) 489 for the NSW Far South Coast is currently suspended until early 2019.<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rdafsc.com.au\/srs-489\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.rdafsc.com.au\/srs-489\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Mid North Coast<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed.\u00a0All applications are currently on hold and RDA MNC is not accepting any further applications due to a high volume of Expressions of Interest.<br \/>\n<a href=\"http:\/\/rdamnc.org.au\/migration\/skilled-regional-sponsored-visa-489\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http:\/\/rdamnc.org.au\/migration\/skilled-regional-sponsored-visa-489\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Murray<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: green; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Open for nominations<br \/>\n<a href=\"http:\/\/www.rdamurray.org.au\/index.php\/migration-services\/skilled-migration\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http:\/\/www.rdamurray.org.au\/index.php\/migration-services\/skilled-migration\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Northern Inland<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: green; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Open for nominations<br \/>\n<a href=\"http:\/\/www.rdani.org.au\/skilled-migration\/skilled-regional-nsw-sponsorship.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http:\/\/www.rdani.org.au\/skilled-migration\/skilled-regional-nsw-sponsorship.php<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Northern Rivers<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/rdanorthernrivers.org.au\/rsms-certification\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/rdanorthernrivers.org.au\/rsms-certification\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Orana<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rdaorana.org.au\/migration\/migrants\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.rdaorana.org.au\/migration\/migrants\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Riverina<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: red; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Temporarily closed.\u00a0Nomination to all occupations are closed. This will be reviewed in February 2019.<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/rdariverina.org.au\/skilled-migration\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/rdariverina.org.au\/skilled-migration\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Southern Inland<\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: green; padding: 0px 5px;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span> Open for nominations<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rdasi.org.au\/regional-migration\/state-sponsored-migration-489-visa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.rdasi.org.au\/regional-migration\/state-sponsored-migration-489-visa\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Note that this information is\u00a0accurate as of\u00a0the\u00a0date of the publication of this post. For <strong>up-to-date information<\/strong> on occupation lists go to our <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/search\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">searching tool<\/a>.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][divider line_type=&#8221;No Line&#8221; custom_height=&#8221;20&#8243;][nectar_global_section id=&#8221;109315&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row type=&#8221;in_container&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; text_color=&#8221;dark&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; row_border_radius_applies=&#8221;bg&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; shape_divider_position=&#8221;bottom&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221;][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221;&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":59824,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[118,92,129],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-33674","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-migration-program","8":"category-nsw","9":"category-skilled-visa"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33674","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.anzs